00:32:57,950 --> 00:33:27,245
body worn cameras aren't turned on or off. So it would be helpful to see whether those whether that's getting improved or not. And, um, are there instances of special notification forms being issued? Um, you asked a lot of our questions. Counselor Callahan. So thank you. I think the only other question we have is, has there ever been an instance of an officer who is allowed to review footage

