00:33:58,919 --> 00:34:22,763
Thank you. I'm just checking on Zoom for any other comments. Seeing none, go back to the podium. For short people. And you can give your name for the record, please. Barry Ingber, 9 Draper Street in Medford. I guess I have a question on process for the chair first.

