00:35:45,603 --> 00:36:13,328
and wondering if there were any exigent uses of those technologies, which is an exception granted in CCOPS. So that's the first set of questions. What was the second part? Any what uses? Whether there were any exigent. Exigent. Yeah. Second set of questions is around the GPS tracker.

