I just want to say Medford People Power doesn't necessarily object to the acquisition of this data in pursuit of a criminal investigation, but we have questions about it. We'd like to know, and I think that Chief Buckley hinted at the answer that we want to hear, but it wasn't clear, was the data only on specific vehicles or was it

